{"tid":1447260,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今晚既事我地唔可以當乜事都冇！聽日全民黑衣連儂人！","createTime":"2019-08-11T15:43:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T16:11:27.000Z","uid":91236,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"cddff2b31c9f579d1e27f39f3b29e241533305d7","tid":1447260,"uid":91236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:43:28.000Z","msg":"今晚大家有眼見真係好撚黑暗<br />\n唔係721果種俾黑社會打既黑暗<br />\n係班黑警已經痴撚晒線<br />\n係唔同既區到用賤招<br />\n完全唔撚當示威者係人咁打<br />\n屌佢地老母 當我地出氣袋？<br />\n<br />\n詳見：<br />\n我敢講今日係自成個運動以黎最黑暗既一日<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1446401\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1446401</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n［民間記者會同文宣組入］我地手揸大量核彈<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1446118\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1446118</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n今日三大核彈<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1446082\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1446082</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n我冇咩好橋 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">我淨係知唔可以當咩事都冇發生<br />\n聽日如常番工！</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>請求大家 聽日全民黑衣<br />\n一人一張文宣貼係身/袋</strong></span><br />\n</span><br />\n而家好多人都唔開airdrop(因為覺得煩）<br />\n收得airdrop都係自己友<br />\n而且airdrop只限iphone<br />\n我地每個人都要做連儂人<br />\n要講俾訓唔撚醒 同藍絲知今晚既事！<br />\n<br />\n先自貼一限<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kyjqeBV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkyjqeBV.png&h=7f8d69c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n下面一路貼文宣<br />\n一路推<br />\n請大家at least print一張出黎！"},{"pid":"271ce1f4a8b6dc50cb91f7df81ad400fa7cd2fcf","tid":1447260,"uid":91236,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:45:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vufABRj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvufABRj.jpg&h=b7a18e65&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d9fb8c46baccc61577e69f2fc67688876a54e46b","tid":1447260,"uid":91236,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"cite